  lines:
  - "While the Chinese experimented vastly for centuries on explosive powders, the
    breakthrough in the discovery of gunpowder appears to have been made by a group
    of alchemists who were in the search for an \u201Celixir of life\u201D."
  - "They manufactured a mixture of sulfur, charcoal and saltpeter that would explode\_when\_ignited."
  textSpeed: 0.02
